1. download smali-1.2.3.jar and baksmali-1.2.3.jar into this directory
  from http://code.google.com/p/smali/downloads/list

2. download codeauroa/donut source
  cd ca-donut
  ./downloadRepo
  if downloadRepo gives an xml error
   open .repo/manifests/default.xml in an editor 
   and change 
   <project path="build" name="platform/build" \>
   into
   <project path="build" name="platform/build" >
   then run ./downloadRepo again

3. build the source:
  cd ca-donut
  ./doBuild

4. build boot.img
  goto my-boot and read README

4. build system.img
  goto my-system and read README
